title: Why is a video of SpaceX Falcon 9 launch being whatsapp shared as Chandrayaan 3?
selftext: Recently there has been a viral whatsapp share showing a footage of SpaceX Falcon 9 launch mentioning it as Chandrayaan 3 launch as seen from phone. It doesnt even make sense, why fake it if real footage is available? There is a footage of actual chandrayaan 3 from a plane ([Link](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fxeFGBv-sFI)), then there is one footage shared here from IIT Madras. It baffles me that those are not shared and instead a fake is being forwarded.
comments: Guess some people are really over the moon for both space launches, they're just trying to cover all their bases! https://motornewz.com/2023/07/18/spacexs-falcon-9-successfully-launches-starlink-mission-sets-stage-for-gen-2-satellites/
